(January 19,1962)

In decisions Nos. 1-8: Present — Bergan, P. J., Coon, Gibson, Herlihy anil Reynolds, JJ.

(A) In the Matter of the Claim of Joann Skinner, Appellant, v. Tobin Packing Co., Inc., et al., Respondents. Workmen’s Compensation Board, Respondent. (B) In the Matter of the Claim of Isaac Solnoitz, Respondent, v. Cook ’N Bull Cafe et al., Appellants. Workmen’s Compensation Board, Respondent.

[In each action] Appeals dismissed unless appellants shall file and serve records, briefs and notes of issue for the March 1962 Term on or before February 26, 1962 in which event motions denied.
